    <!-- EN: Subcore -->
    <AE_Subcore.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.AnomalyLabel>人格子核</AE_Subcore.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.AnomalyLabel>
    <!-- EN: A device which resembles a standart subcore or a persona core, although completely different in design -->
    <AE_Subcore.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.AnomalyDesc>外觀類似於標準的次生核心或人格核心的裝置，儘管在設計上完全不同。</AE_Subcore.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.AnomalyDesc>
    <!-- EN: #1/? Subcore study report -->
    <AE_Subcore.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.label>#1/? 人格子核研究報告</AE_Subcore.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.label>
    <!--
        EN: General properties of the Subcore\n\nSubject: {PAWN_nameDef}\n\nAbstract:\nThis report details observations from Subject {PAWN_nameDef} regarding the visible properties of the newfound device we decided to name "Subcore", due to it's resemblance to those objects. On the outside it seems to be made of some unknown black alloy. The feature that strikes us the most is it's symbol, which is glowing despite the object being disconnected from any power source, suggesting it to be powered from the outside. Any attempts to look inside of the object proved futile, as the surface seems to be incredibly tough. However, the object also has cables protruding from it's insides, which allows us to connect the device to a computer and try to gather some data from the device.\n\nObservations:\n{PAWN_nameDef} Reported the object to be resembling a subcore or a persona core.\nThe casing is made of an unknown and incredibly sturdy alloy.\nSeems to be powered from the inside.\n\nFindings:\nIt seems to be possible to extract data from the device if we connect it to a computer.\n\nDiscussion:\nAll of the valuable data seems to be packed inside of the device, because of that we first need a way to get it out.\n\nRecommendations:\nConnection to a computer or other similar device is required.
    -->
    <AE_Subcore.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.text>人格子核的一般性質\n\n對象：{PAWN_nameDef}\n\n摘要：\n本報告詳細記錄了對象{PAWN_nameDef}關於我們新發現裝置的可見屬性的觀察結果，因其與人格核心或次核的相似性，決定將其命名爲“人格子核”。從外部看，它似乎是由某種未知的黑色合金製成。最引人注目的特徵是其上的符號，儘管該物體與沒有與任何電源連接，但符號仍在發光，這表明它可能從外部獲得能量。試圖查看物體內部的任何嘗試都證明是徒勞的，因爲表面似乎非常堅固。然而，物體也有從內部伸出的電纜，這允許我們將設備連接到計算機上，並嘗試從設備中收集一些數據。\n\n現象：\n{PAWN_nameDef}報告裝置類似於次核或人格核心。\n外殼由一種不知名的堅固合金製成。\n裝置似乎由內部供電。\n\n發現：\n如果我們將其連接到電腦上，似乎可以從中中提取數據。\n\n討論：\n所有有價值的數據似乎都在設備內部，因此我們首先需要找到一種方法將其導出。\n\n建議：\n需要將該裝置連接電腦或其他類似設備。</AE_Subcore.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.text>

