    <AE_SubcoreConnected.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.AnomalyLabel>子核終端</AE_SubcoreConnected.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.AnomalyLabel>
    <!-- EN: The terminal which is connected to the strange subcore, allowing us to gather data and even communicate with it -->
    <AE_SubcoreConnected.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.AnomalyDesc>與人格子核相連的終端，使我們能夠收集數據，甚至與之通信</AE_SubcoreConnected.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.AnomalyDesc>
    <!-- EN: #2/? Subcore study report -->
    <AE_SubcoreConnected.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.label>#2/? 人格子核研究報告</AE_SubcoreConnected.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.label>
    <!-- EN: Data extracted from the subcore\n\nSubject: {PAWN_nameDef}\n\nAbstract:\nThis report details the data recovered from the subcore by the Subject {PAWN_nameDef}. First attempts to extract any data have proved futile, as the machinery behind the Subcore seems to be way more advanced than we have imagined. However, after some time we have finally succeded to connect, or to be more precise, the being inside has succeded, as that seemed to have happened by itself rather than through our actions. The being inside did not have a name before our intrusion, but for the purpose of communication it decided to call itself Ion. Despite it being way more powerful than we are, it still communicated with us and even gave us an offering. Because it, as it tells us, does not have a body and is incapable of manipulating the world around it, it has decided that cooperation is the best course of action for now. It wants us to leave it unharmed, for the price of the data it has, which supposedly contains a way for us to connect to a higher being that created Ion. After those words it proceeded to unlock the files for us, which we now can study.\n\nObservations:\nThe being has allowed us to communicate with it.\nIt decided to cooperate with us, after which it gave us information.\nThe data seemingly contains a way to connect with a higher being.\n\nFindings:\nValuable information, including a way to connect to an archopersona.\n\nDiscussion:\nBecause the being is trapped in the subcore and is incapable of doing any harm, and also gave us valuable data, we don't yet have a reason to consider the research risky.\n\nRecommendations:\nExtract data from the device. -->
    <AE_SubcoreConnected.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.text>從子核中提取出數據\n\n對象：{PAWN_nameDef}\n\n摘要：\n本報告詳細記錄了對象{PAWN_nameDef}從子核中提取的數據。由於子核心背後的原理似乎比我們想象的要先進得多，最初嘗試提取任何數據都證明是徒勞的。過了一段時間後，我們終於成功連接，或者更準確地說，是內部的實體允許我們連接，因爲連接的建立看起來是自行發生的，而非通過我們的行動。內部的實體在我們侵入之前沒有名字，但爲了交流的方便，它決定稱自己爲Ion。儘管它比我們強大得多，卻仍然與我們交流，甚至給了我們一份禮物。因爲Ion告訴我們，它沒有身體，無法操縱周圍的世界，於是認爲當下與我們合作是最好的行動方針。Ion希望我們不傷害它，作爲交換，Ion提供了它所擁有的數據，據稱這些數據包含了我們與創造了Ion的高級生物連接的方法。說完這些話後，它繼續爲我們解鎖文件，現在我們可以研究這些文件了。\n\n現象：\n內部實體允許我們與其連接。\n爲我們提供信息後，其決定與我們合作。\n數據似乎包含與一更高等級實體交流的方法。\n\n發現：\n數據十分有價值，其中包含一種連接超凡人格的方式。\n\n討論：\n由於該實體被困在子核中，沒有能力造成任何傷害，並且還爲我們提供了寶貴的數據，因此我們還沒有理由認爲這項研究是有風險的。\n\n建議：\n繼續提取數據。</AE_SubcoreConnected.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.text>

